subject: Basketball

Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Jordan Taylor struggled on offense much of the game but drove the lane and sank a jumper with 32 seconds left to seal visiting Wisconsin’s 67-63 victory over No. 22 Illinois on Sunday.
